---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Join the Club">
  
  <div class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-16 px-4 rounded-b-3xl md:rounded-2xl mb-12 shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-96 h-96 bg-primary opacity-20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Become a Member</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Join a community of passionate aviators. Whether you are a seasoned pilot or have never held a transmitter, you are welcome here.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Community & Learning</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Learn from experienced builders and pilots. Free flight instruction for beginners.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Safe Flying Site</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Access to our private, insured OTX AeroDrome with bermuda runway and covered pits.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Events & Fun</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Participate in fly-ins, swap meets, and club cookouts throughout the year.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">How to Join (3 Simple Steps)</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md border-l-8 border-primary">
          <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-primary text-white font-bold text-xl rounded-full">1</div>
          <div class="grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Join the AMA</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              All members must hold a current membership with the Academy of Model Aeronautics (AMA) for insurance purposes.
            </p>
            <a 
              href="https://www.modelaircraft.org/join" 
              target="_blank"
              class="inline-block text-sm font-bold text-primary hover:text-primary-hover underline"
            >
              Sign up at ModelAircraft.org &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md border-l-8 border-blue-500">
          <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold text-xl rounded-full">2</div>
          <div class="grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Complete FAA TRUST Test</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              The FAA requires all recreational drone and RC pilots to pass "The Recreational UAS Safety Test" (TRUST). It is free, online, and impossible to fail.
            </p>
            <a 
              href="https://trust.modelaircraft.org/" 
              target="_blank"
              class="inline-block text-sm font-bold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline"
            >
              Take the Free Test Here &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md border-l-8 border-green-500">
          <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-green-500 text-white font-bold text-xl rounded-full">3</div>
          <div class="grow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Submit Application & Dues</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Download our membership application, fill it out, and bring it to the next club meeting or mail it in.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
              <a 
                href="/assets/documents/membership-application.pdf" 
                download
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
                </svg>
                Download PDF
              </a>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 self-center italic">or bring cash/check to the field</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">Annual Membership Dues</h2>
      <div class="overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm rounded-xl border border-gray-200">
        <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
          <thead class="bg-gray-50">
            <tr>
              <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Membership Type</th>
              <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Description</th>
              <th scope="col" class="px-6 py-3 text-right text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Annual Cost</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap font-bold text-gray-900">Open Membership</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Standard adult membership (Ages 19 and older)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-right font-bold text-primary">$100.00</td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap font-bold text-gray-900">Junior Membership</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 text-gray-600">Pilots under age 19 (Must have AMA)</td>
              <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-right font-bold text-green-600">$10</td>
            </tr>

          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <!-- <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2 text-center">* New members also pay a one-time $25 initiation fee.</p> -->
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do I need to own a plane to start?
            <span class="text-primary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            No! We highly recommend you do NOT buy a plane until you talk to us. We offer introductory flights with club trainer planes using a "buddy box" system, so you can try flying risk-free before spending any money.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do you fly drones/quadcopters?
            <span class="text-primary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Yes, we welcome all types of RC aircraft including fixed-wing, helicopters, and multi-rotors (drones). We ask that FPV pilots have a spotter present for safety.
          </p>
        </details>

        <details class="group bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-4 cursor-pointer">
          <summary class="font-bold text-gray-800 list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            When are meetings held?
            <span class="text-primary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">▼</span>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
            Club meetings are typically held on the first Saturday of the month at the field (weather permitting) or at a local library during winter. Check the Events page for the latest schedule.
          </p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>